        'Electric motors are much more efficient than petrol engines — about 90% of the electricity used actually moves the car, compared to only 20–40% for a petrol engine.',
        'EVs have fewer moving parts than petrol cars — no gearbox, exhaust, fuel pump, or oil filter — meaning they need far less maintenance.',
